1.2 Per-File Purpose Summary
File	What It Tests
test_axis_stability.py	13-axis Mnemosyne audit -- verifies all 13 memory axes are operational (episodic, procedural, goal, temporal, spatial, semantic, operational, meta-cog, creative, rational, verification, efficiency, cross-session). Largest test file at 135 lines.
test_full_pipeline.py	End-to-end pipeline test importing from sophia, mnemosyne, architrave, atropos, morpheus. Checks draft/critique/refine flow, tool validation, temperature profiles, state bus, context assembly.
test_phase_11_9_integrity.py	Governance file integrity -- checks AGENTS.md, GEMINI.md, .cursorrules, version strings, symlinks, .gitignore, PYTHONPATH, YAML validity, database schemas, VRAM constraints, and spatial mapper health.
test_sovereign_truth_guard.py	Shadow verification system -- tests VRAM lie detection, blacklisted model rejection, output guard enforcement, hallucination spiral prevention, deadlock resolver routing.
test_vision_pipeline.py	Axis 14 vision pipeline -- tests image optimization, VisualStore (store/query/retention), tier routing for vision tasks, and gnosis context assembly for Axis 14.
test_two_pass_verification.py	L3 two-pass verification -- tests evaluator zones, hallucination detection (contradictory code), citation scoring, krisis should_continue routing after failed audits.
test_pruning_rules.py	VRAM sweeper pruning -- tests 30-day retention pruning on operational_logs, spatial_cache, and failure_memory tables.
test_temporal_validity.py	Axis 4 temporal validity -- tests event_key supersede lifecycle, get_fact_at() temporal queries, fact history ordering with timestamps.
test_axis11_logic.py	Axis 11 Z3/SymPy formal verification -- tests agent hierarchy consistency (L1->L2 execution gate), tool authorization logic, resource bounds, state transition rules.
test_hermes_bridge.py	Cross-session Hermes CLI bridge -- tests init, save, load, search, list, close, and error handling via subprocess calls to scripts/hermes_cli.py.
test_verification_gate.py	Hard gate verification -- tests contradiction detection in verify_node, output guard enforcement, reranker integration, and should_continue routing.
test_hybrid_search_rrf.py	Axis 6 hybrid search -- tests Nomic embedding + FTS with RRF merge ranking, including text seeding and result relevance validation.
test_tool_bridge.py	ToolBridge dispatcher -- tests ls execution, read/glob/grep tool calls, error handling, and timeout enforcement.
test_failure_pruning.py	Failure memory aging/pruning -- inserts old/recent failure records, tests sweeper's prune logic against aged entries.
test_failure_memory_unit.py	Axis 8 failure memory unit tests -- tests rule validation (min length 50), SHA-256 dedup, recurrence counting, severity tracking.
test_failure_memory_integration.py	Gnosis integration with failure memory -- tests get_dynamic_context() injection of failure rules into Sophia's context.
test_sandbox.py	LightSandbox isolated code execution -- tests basic execution, timeout enforcement, dangerous import blocking, cleanup.
test_vram_scheduler.py	VRAM model fitting and monitoring -- tests find_fitting_model capability-based selection, GPU memory info, token budget, context pruning.
test_evaluator_grading.py	AdversarialEvaluator 6-pillar grading -- tests empty drafts, good drafts, citation scoring, safety checks, structured output validation.
test_citation_guard.py	[SRC:axis_N] citation consistency -- tests citation scoring, missing citations, fake citation detection, partial drafts.
test_security_utils.py	API key validation and secret loading -- tests Gemini key format validation, keyring secret loading, env var population.
test_langgraph_trace.py	LangGraph reflection trace -- tests create_clotho_graph() state machine initialization and reflection node invocation.
stability_check_phase_11_18_1.py	AgnosticArchitrave stability -- tests async generation flow with gateway proxy, gateway URL env var configuration.
test_ankyra_v2.py	Ankyra v2 anchor persistence -- tests DB logging to mnemosyne.db, logging handler write verification.
test_phase_11_18_14.py	Tier 0 routing and math LLM intent -- tests ultra-light tier routing, should_call_tools, SymPy math verification detection.
test_reflection_quality.py	ReflectionStore quality filters -- tests minimum length enforcement (50 chars), entity frequency tracking, dedup logic.
test_router.py	TaskRouter capability classification -- tests task-to-category routing (code, math, reasoning, chat) and state_bus message passing.
test_tool_validator.py	ToolValidator JSON schema validation -- tests valid JSON, missing keys, strict mode enforcement.
test_mnemosyne_stores.py	Core memory stores -- tests EpisodicStore (log/recent), GoalStore (add/list_active/complete), ProceduralStore (record_usage/get_patterns), MetaCognition (reliability tracking), RationalStore (fact storage).
test_entity_pipeline.py	EntityExtractor -- tests entity extraction from technical text, relation logic stubs.
test_gemini_context_cache.py	Gemini context caching -- tests cache creation with system instruction, requires live GEMINI_API_KEY.
test_context_hardening.py	CodebaseMapper env loading, RAG chunk limits, SemanticStore search limits.
test_agnostic_gateway.py	AgnosticArchitrave initialization -- tests sovereign mode flag, default model resolution via resolve_capability().
